      private void url_handler​(File dic, String url) throws UndersizeException, UnbalncedException, FileNotFoundException
      private function that handles dictionairy constraction from a json file pointed at by the url variable it expects the json to contain a field with the name "description" that is either a string or it contains a fied called "value" that is a string
      Parameters:
      dic - file that the dictionairy will be stored at
      url - url to look up, must be to a json file
      Throws:
      UndersizeException
      UnbalncedException
      FileNotFoundException

      Returns:
      string from "description":"value" or "description"
